{"tid":894934,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"用pccw 網上行 嘅人 同職員入一入黎 好撚燥","createTime":"2018-11-08T18:20:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T00:17:49.000Z","uid":86844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aca9f94e07ad3ff7b75acad6bb10d711512d8121","tid":894934,"uid":86844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T18:20:10.000Z","msg":"咁我本身就用緊PCCW上網嘅<br />\n咁佢間公司就成日都cut 我上網<br />\n之後次次打電話佢都話我之前冇交到月費<br />\n但屋企人每次都有準時交到月費 所以一直冇理佢見到佢有用到 但係間唔中都會無啦啦cut我上網<br />\n但今次真係頂唔撚順 上佢個網度睇返啲月費資料佢有冇講到我以前幾時冇交月費<br />\n仲無啦啦收咗兩舊水重新啟用上網費用<br />\n之後對對下張單發現唔對路<br />\n明明冇交一期月費但佢嗰個previous charge 越滾越大<br />\n之後無啦啦又收多咗兩舊水<br />\n好撚燥 有冇人知可以點樣搞掂佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oXNjy9C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoXNjy9C.png&h=e516d482&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e2OyDBi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe2OyDBi.png&h=287176da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sk6o0PE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsk6o0PE.png&h=14f3b178&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/USAUn20.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUSAUn20.png&h=d7c0479a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d4e33f65c770847d3bf3eaa6d0ba67d0befd8ff","tid":894934,"uid":128595,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T18:27:24.000Z","msg":"要查單就直接打去/HKT CS FACEBOOK問啦,<br />\n<br />\n遮D唔遮D,<br />\n你BARCODE下面頭14個字咪你個AC NO."},{"pid":"1e82924d2f77e0022fdb56ae4d8fab19e9c004e4","tid":894934,"uid":170015,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T18:30:33.000Z","msg":"你第一張單已經無交到$4xx 個條數，<br />\n另外第二張單已經係交錯，月費$266你交得$226<br />\n<br />\n你不斷都係欠緊，你不如打上去問你究竟邊個月無交到，正常就係你清左條數就唔會收你reconnection fee，但你應該唔只一次係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76a959e0d79164b0a5aa0892f2817ebd215410e","tid":894934,"uid":170015,"like":6,"dislike":0,"sc